tyle=\"font-size: medium;\">(打狗同還手唔計)</span> 不入禁區</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:31:49.000Z","msg":"岩 凡事都要睇情況<br />\n如果手捉比狗咬緊可無視條件，即刻救人"},{"pid":"1b41e9991eefd97129d92dd3c193243a53d998b1","tid":1468370,"uid":85290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:32:19.000Z","msg":"今晚機場單野，大家真係要醒 | LIHKG<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1468119/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1468119/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"f8a73d784e392cfa5084e50cb4a78dd02fd8088e","tid":1468370,"uid":123082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:39:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cf5a55fd858a19d1343f35ed86ae4885a020408","tid":1468370,"uid":268373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:39:48.000Z","msg":"我 正 式 宣 布 ！今晚黑警想上前毆打路過女遊客，示威者勇武拯救<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1468010\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1468010</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ef82d56b137ccd679324e3edbe53df6560501870","tid":1468370,"uid":123082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:49:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54ab9c5a0fa32529a01a16a253b13cb5809cf4eb","tid":1468370,"uid":6363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:50:09.000Z","msg":"大家聽住。<br />\n知唔知點解政府811咁撚豬會畀你地影到示威者入面有鬼？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而唔繼續鬼落去<br />\n<br />\n其實佢地呢招好撚高，政府知我地核彈都唔撚割。所以特登話你知：我地放咗鬼喺你度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n等你次次都疑神疑鬼，等戰友間失去咗互相信任。<br />\n<br />\n大家諗吓，由612 走到而家，我地本住一句核彈都唔割先得。所以，所有檢討post，要等該日完咗先好出。仲有唔好懷疑自己身邊嘅人，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">戰友總畀警鬼多</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不割蓆、不譴責、不篤灰、不分化、不捉鬼<br />\n</span></strong></strong></span>"},{"pid":"9f0c1c5ef648d27b46de8cb268f606c176f9a101","tid":1468370,"uid":123082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:59:47.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5e6e950bc04133154a2adfd0ddd650717b13a79","tid":1468370,"uid":123082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:10:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}